as\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"5000 residents\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"an abundance\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"towering cliffs\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's possible to get here on foot from Nice along the coast path.\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2605, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.518701448890417e-22, \"text\": \"Nice\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"foot\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"the coast path\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The beach is small but, if it gets crowded, bask on one of the rocks, where you can jump straight into crystal cool water and sizzle on the stone like a frying egg afterwards.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The beach\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"the rocks\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"crystal cool water\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"the stone\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"a frying egg\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laid-back little beach restaurants sell fresh seafood and arancini.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2866, \"end\": 2874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arancini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"arancini\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arancini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arancini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Laid-back little beach restaurants\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2842}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh seafood\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How to get there:The closestairportis Nice, a 20-minute train ride f